node.text: Eid mubarak! Eid with new clothes, handmade by @ditut, made from used and vintage materials (tableclothes, tea towels, pillowcases) #eidmubarak #eid

Indonesian eid festivity with Macintosh 128K & MacPaint. #eidmubarak #eid2021 

Bedug - a large double barreled drum with buffalo leather.

Ketupat - practically made from rice, packed in a diamond shaped container of woven palm leaf pouch.

Opor - chicken cooked in coconut milk with mixture of the spice include galangal, lemongrass, cinnamon, palm sugar, coriander, cumin, candlenut, garlic, shallot & pepper.
